10px;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><strong>Programming note:</strong><em> Money S=
tuff will be off tomorrow, back on Monday.</em></p>
<table class=3D"header" width=3D"100%" border=3D"0" cellspacing=3D"0" cellp=
adding=3D"0">
<tr>
<td class=3D"body-header-container" style=3D"border-collapse: collapse; mso=
-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt;">
<h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Arial=
, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">ChatGPT</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/30369314.268448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud2lyZWQuY29tL3N0b3J5L2NoYXRn=
cHQtZmx1ZW50LWJzLw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB7614f877" itemprop=3D"StoryLink=
" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-d=
ecoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: =
#000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> stereotype</=
a> of <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30369314.268=
448/aHR0cHM6Ly9vcGVuYWkuY29tL2Jsb2cvY2hhdGdwdC8/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB6c=
31dae9" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" st=
yle=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-widt=
h: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgroun=
d-color: #ccc;"> ChatGPT</a>, Open AI=E2=80=99s publicly available conversa=
tional large language model, is that if you ask it a technical question it =
will give you an answer that is confident and plausible but not necessarily=
 correct. This is of course an <em>incredibly=C2=A0</em>useful skill, and a=
 very good model of a certain sort of human intelligence; ChatGPT seems dan=
gerous as a software engineer but could have a good run as an investment ba=
nker.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-1" style=3D"color: #0000=
00; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bott=
om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: =
transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[1]</span>
</a></p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">How is it as an asset manager, or at least an =
asset-management salesrobot? Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Sam Potter and Katherine G=
reifeld <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30369314.2=
68448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDEtMjYvd=
2UtYXNrZWQtY2hhdGdwdC10by1tYWtlLWEtbWFya2V0LWJlYXRpbmctZXRmLWhlcmUtcy10aGUt=
cmVzdWx0P2NtcGlkPUJCRDAxMjYyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3N=
vdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDEyNiZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg=
/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBd10418f8" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"ite=
mscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !i=
mportant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bo=
ttom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  gave it a go</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In a bid to see how close technology really is=
 to replacing Wall Street=E2=80=99s army of analysts, experts and money run=
ners, we challenged ChatGPT, the artificial intelligence tool that=E2=80=99=
s taking the internet by storm, to create us a winning portfolio for the US=
 stock market.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The result: A classic exercise in fence-sittin=
g, with the tool explaining that the market is too unpredictable to design =
such a fund, while warning about the need to pick investments aligning with=
 our goals and appetite for risk-taking.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIt is not possible for me to design a=
n ETF that will beat the US stock market because the stock market is unpred=
ictable and past performance does not guarantee future results,=E2=80=9D Ch=
atGPT says, disappointingly, adding a bunch of not-investing-advice boilerp=
late. Bleh. I would have expected more unearned confidence. Like I=E2=80=99=
d expect it to come up with a list of 50 tickers, no problem; I just wouldn=
=E2=80=99t expect them to beat the market, and maybe a couple of them would=
 not correspond to actual stocks.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You can do better, where by =E2=80=9Cbetter=E2=
=80=9D I mean =E2=80=9Cget more confident answers out of ChatGPT=E2=80=9D r=
ather than =E2=80=9Cactually get it to beat the market for you.=E2=80=9D La=
st month <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30369314.=
268448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZnQuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvOTY4YWU2Y2QtMjQ4NS00YWIwLWIwZDEt=
ZWIyMDZmNTk4ODRh/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB650d229a" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" =
itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-dec=
oration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0=
00000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Robin Wigglesw=
orth at the Financial Times</a> wrote about a quantitative research analyst=
 who got ChatGPT to write research notes for him; they were, you know, adeq=
uate.=C2=A0And I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/3=
0369314.268448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIw=
MjAtMDEtMDcvbm8tcnVzaC1yZXBheWluZy10aGVzZS1zdHVkZW50LWxvYW5zP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA=
xMjYyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJn=
V0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDEyNiZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a2=
3cB6d802c0a" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blan=
k" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom=
-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; back=
ground-color: #ccc;">  once wrote</a> about GPT-2, an earlier large languag=
e model:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you trained it on a bunch of Warren Buffett=
 annual letters maybe it would say some stuff that sounds like Warren Buffe=
tt? Not just in terms of=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusines=
s.com/click/30369314.268448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuaW5kZXBlbmRlbnQuY28udWsvbmV3cy9=
idXNpbmVzcy9uZXdzL3dhcnJlbi1idWZmZXR0LXNleC1leHBsYWluLWludmVzdG1lbnQtZmluYW=
5jZS13b21lbi15ZXMtYmlsbGlvbmFpcmUtYmVya3NoaXJlLWhhdGhhd2F5LW1pc29neW55LWE3N=
jA1MTcxLmh0bWw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB82b0ec39" target=3D"_blank" style=
=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;">folksy sex jokes</a>=C2=A0but also in terms of penetrating inv=
estment insight? Maybe GPT-2 would digest Buffett=E2=80=99s mind, or rather=
 specifically the parts of Buffett=E2=80=99s mind that are exposed when he =
writes prose, and it would use that understanding of his mind to write Buff=
ett-like prose recommending Buffett-like investing decisions?</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Or if you run an investment firm and you=E2=80=
=99ve got a corpus of memos from your analysts recommending investment deci=
sions, why not take the memos that=C2=A0<em>worked out</em>=E2=80=94the one=
s recommending investments that went up=E2=80=94and feed them into GPT-2? T=
hen have it write you a new memo and see if it=E2=80=99s any good?</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I wouldn=E2=80=99t bet on it or anything; it=
=E2=80=99s interesting to speculate about, but it seems unlikely that a com=
puter will get good at=C2=A0<em>making </em>investment decisions just by in=
gesting how humans have=C2=A0<em>articulated=C2=A0</em>investment=C2=A0deci=
sions. (It=E2=80=99s much more likely to fixate on boilerplate about how =
=E2=80=9Cpast performance does not guarantee future results.=E2=80=9D) But =
I bet a computer could get pretty good at=C2=A0<em>articulating=C2=A0</em>i=
nvestment decisions from that training set. (In a sense this is the opposit=
e of a classic =E2=80=9Cblack box=E2=80=9D machine-learning investment algo=
rithm: Classic quant signals might work, but <a href=3D"https://link.mail.b=
loombergbusiness.com/click/30369314.268448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNv=
bS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTYtMTEtMjEvcmVuYWlzc2FuY2Utcy1za2lsbC1hbmQtZmF=
jZWJvb2stcy1idXliYWNrP2NtcGlkPUJCRDAxMjYyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW=
1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDEyNiZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249b=
W9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB73b00fbd" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" ite=
mscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decora=
tion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0000=
00; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">
you can=E2=80=99t explain them</a>; ChatGPT might not work, but it can expl=
ain itself.)=C2=A0If your hedge fund lost money last year, maybe ask ChatGP=
T to write your investor letter for you. It can spin up some platitudes, qu=
ote some Stoic philosophers, and sound confident and plausible, which is al=
l you really need for the=C2=A0<em>letter</em>.=C2=A0</p>
