ct to the internet using your device.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5p=
x;">And then =E2=80=94=C2=A0this is the crypto part =E2=80=94=C2=A0<em>they=
=C2=A0</em>pay for using the coverage you provide, and=C2=A0<em>you=C2=A0</=
em>get paid for that coverage, in the project=E2=80=99s crypto tokens.</li>
</ul>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Why don=E2=80=99t they just pay in dollars? Wh=
y don=E2=80=99t you just get paid in dollars? Well! Because, as I have <a h=
ref=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30369314.268448/aHR0cH=
M6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMTItMjEvdGhlcmUtc=
y1pbnNpZGUtaW5mb3JtYXRpb24taW4tc2VjLWZpbGluZ3M_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDEyNjIzX01PTkVZ=
U1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjM=
