<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/30369314.268448/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2Fyd=
